194
00:14:27,730 --> 00:14:30,563
Just the thought of not seeing you

195
00:14:30,797 --> 00:14:33,470
and your face again in this life,

196
00:14:34,763 --> 00:14:36,810
I just couldn't handle it.

197
00:14:39,603 --> 00:14:41,603
