200
00:14:51,477 --> 00:14:53,664
how much I love you?

201
00:14:54,770 --> 00:14:55,770
I know.

202
00:14:56,717 --> 00:14:58,040
I know, Dech.

203
00:15:04,417 --> 00:15:05,817
I love you too.

204
00:15:15,817 --> 00:15:16,840
Thank you.

205
00:15:23,470 --> 00:15:26,400
My intention was to
make merit for Saeng and Chaem.

206
00:15:28,210 --> 00:15:30,360
This shouldn't have happened, Dech.

207
00:15:32,623 --> 00:15:35,280
The fact that you and Fueang
were going to make merit,

208
00:15:35,790 --> 00:15:37,120
who knew about it, ma'am?

209
00:15:40,090 --> 00:15:41,090
Well...

210
00:15:42,110 --> 00:15:43,400
the whole house knew.

211
00:15:46,403 --> 00:15:48,559
Because everyone helped me
prepare the offerings.

212
00:15:48,570 --> 00:15:51,360
They all wanted to make merit
for Saeng and Chaem too.

213
00:15:57,897 --> 00:15:59,080
You should rest.

214
00:16:00,803 --> 00:16:02,323
I have something to take care of.

215
00:16:54,717 --> 00:16:56,584
Dech, you dare to slap me?!

216
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:59,883
Don't think I'll let you hurt me
without a fight, slave!

217
00:16:59,970 --> 00:17:01,040
Enough!

218
00:17:01,676 --> 00:17:02,676
Or you want more?

219
00:17:03,863 --> 00:17:05,259
What the hell is wrong the you?!

220
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:06,400
This is nothing

221
00:17:06,663 --> 00:17:08,720
compared to your attempt
to kill Ms. Malai!

222
00:17:12,803 --> 00:17:14,443
How did she frame me this time?

223
00:17:14,610 --> 00:17:16,077
Is that why you're accusing me?

224
00:17:16,203 --> 00:17:17,600
She didn't do anything.

225
00:17:17,629 --> 00:17:20,129
She just almost died on her way
to make merit with Fueang.

226
00:17:21,223 --> 00:17:23,800
What does a leaking boat
have anything to do with me?

227
00:17:29,183 --> 00:17:30,680
What did you just say?

228
00:17:32,637 --> 00:17:33,640
I haven't told you

229
00:17:34,237 --> 00:17:35,597
what almost killed Ms. Malai.

230
00:17:36,677 --> 00:17:37,677
Well...

231
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:39,817
She took a boat to make merit
and almost died.

232
00:17:40,143 --> 00:17:41,250
What else could it be?

233
00:17:41,810 --> 00:17:42,840
I was just guessing.

234
00:17:43,610 --> 00:17:46,920
The only one in this house
who wants Ms. Malai dead is you.

235
00:17:48,310 --> 00:17:49,543
You want Fueang dead too.

236
00:17:49,997 --> 00:17:51,997
If it wasn't you, who would it be?

237
00:17:54,530 --> 00:17:56,163
If you plan on hurting Ms. Malai,

238
00:17:56,303 --> 00:17:57,840
I'll leave this place.

239
00:17:58,290 --> 00:17:59,320
I don't believe you.

240
00:17:59,830 --> 00:18:01,637
You stayed because
you want the fortune,

241
00:18:01,843 --> 00:18:02,843
the comfort.

242
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:06,263
And right now
everything is in your control.

243
00:18:06,343 --> 00:18:07,636
Don't talk tough, Dech.

244
00:18:07,990 --> 00:18:11,337
If you think I want
to stay here for the fortune,

245
00:18:11,597 --> 00:18:12,897
you're wrong, ma'am.

246
00:18:13,283 --> 00:18:16,200
