wanted to leave this place.

247
00:18:16,563 --> 00:18:18,000
Then why didn't you?

248
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:19,360
Answer me.

249
00:18:19,517 --> 00:18:21,517
Because I knew if I left,

250
00:18:21,610 --> 00:18:24,200
you'd squander the fortune
down to the last penny.

251
00:18:25,943 --> 00:18:27,320
Before Mueang's grown.

252
00:18:27,657 --> 00:18:28,657
Am I right?

253
00:18:32,157 --> 00:18:34,240
When I run out of patience,

254
00:18:35,537 --> 00:18:37,537
I'd abandon even my own child.

255
00:18:40,130 --> 00:18:42,197
You choose a woman
over your flesh and blood.

256
00:18:42,483 --> 00:18:44,280
Over your benefactor.

257
00:18:44,397 --> 00:18:45,397
No wonder

258
00:18:45,437 --> 00:18:47,790
you dared hurt the viscount
and left him paralyzed.

259
00:18:48,763 --> 00:18:49,763
Ow, Dech.

260
00:18:51,043 --> 00:18:52,760
I didn't hurt the viscount.

261
00:18:54,090 --> 00:18:56,090
If I did what you claim,

262
00:18:56,223 --> 00:18:58,880
I would have killed you
to silence you a long time ago.

263
00:18:59,290 --> 00:19:01,097
Ow, Dech, let go.
You're hurting me.

264
00:19:01,337 --> 00:19:03,600
I stayed because of Ms. Malai.

265
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:05,957
If you try to hurt Ms. Malai again,

266
00:19:07,470 --> 00:19:09,240
