00:21:05,290 --> 00:21:09,414
♪ Ready to be given
to you for good ♪

277
00:21:11,049 --> 00:21:16,984
♪ Here's a life
that's still being offered ♪

278
00:21:17,581 --> 00:21:21,098
♪ To you alone ♪

279
00:21:21,221 --> 00:21:25,553
♪ You might be unaware
and still wondering ♪

280
00:21:25,587 --> 00:21:27,680
Keep playing. I want to hear.

281
00:21:27,713 --> 00:21:33,746
♪ Why I'm willing to do
everything for you ♪

282
00:21:34,041 --> 00:21:36,492
♪ Whatever you want ♪

283
00:21:36,748 --> 00:21:41,392
♪ Everything I've done ♪

284
00:21:41,783 --> 00:21:44,066
♪ What's it for? ♪

285
00:21:44,283 --> 00:21:49,747
♪ I can't give you my reasons ♪

286
00:21:50,142 --> 00:21:55,560
♪ Love has its own reason ♪

287
00:21:55,930 --> 00:22:01,428
♪ I've only done
what my heart wants ♪

288
00:22:01,606 --> 00:22:07,369
♪ All you have to do
is accept my love ♪

289
00:22:12,190 --> 00:22:14,343
Did you want to say something?

290
00:22:16,797 --> 00:22:18,560
I wanted to apologize

291
00:22:19,563 --> 00:22:20,663
for the misunderstanding.

292
00:22:20,850 --> 00:22:21,850
It's okay, ma'am.

293
00:22:22,157 --> 00:22:23,157
I understand.

294
00:22:24,417 --> 00:22:25,640
Are you still mad at me?

295
00:22:34,837 --> 00:22:38,160
I love you too much
to be mad at you.

296
00:23:05,330 --> 00:23:06,517
Malai is stupid.

297
00:23:06,777 --> 00:23:08,284
She's gone back to believe Dech.

298
00:23:08,597 --> 00:23:10,920
I won't let you win
without a fight, Dech!

299
00:23:30,143 --> 00:23:34,634
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

300
00:23:35,056 --> 00:23:39,543
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

301
00:24:01,269 --> 00:24:02,840
You're watching me.

302
00:24:03,130 --> 00:24:04,640
How can I fall as sleep?

303
00:24:05,476 --> 00:24:08,116
I just want to tuck in
the woman I love.

304
00:24:08,410 --> 00:24:11,704
Please let me sit here
until you fall asleep.

305
00:24:14,990 --> 00:24:16,160
Don't worry, ma'am.

306
00:24:16,983 --> 00:24:19,600
I won't do anything
to dishonor you.

307
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:23,120
Once you're asleep,
I'll leave, ma'am.

308
00:24:29,563 --> 00:24:32,640
I'll definitely have
a good dream tonight.

309
00:24:36,917 --> 00:24:38,144
Please dream of me too.

310
00:25:33,057 --> 00:25:36,404
For this kind of money
is worth getting hurt a little.

311
00:25:36,597 --> 00:25:39,314
And please keep it a secret
as we agreed.

312
00:25:41,167 --> 00:25:44,080
Call on me if you have
this kind of job again. I like it.

313
00:25:46,793 --> 00:25:47,880
You must be happy

314
00:25:48,127 --> 00:25:49,800
now that you got back with Malai.

315
00:25:50,023 --> 00:25:51,400
You're quite cunning, Dech.

316
00:25:55,130 --> 00:25:57,757
You want me to help you kill Malai?

317
00:25:58,417 --> 00:26:00,070
You said you loved her so much.

318
00:26:00,370 --> 00:26:01,777
What made you change your mind?

319
00:26:02,037 --> 00:26:03,120
It's just an act.

320
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:05,210
I know you can do it.

321
00:26:06,203 --> 00:26:07,243
Aren't you worried

322
00:26:07,270 --> 00:26:10,280
you might accidentally kill
Malai and Fueang for real?

323
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:12,880
Fueang can swim. She'll survive.

324
00:26:13,490 --> 00:26:16,300
As for Ms. Malai,
I'll follow them closely by boat.

325
00:26:16,393 --> 00:26:18,920
I'll never let Ms. Malai die.

326
00:26:20,793 --> 00:26:23,160
You just have to put on a show.

327
00:26:28,730 --> 00:26:30,730
You don't have to
wait for my answer.

328
00:26:30,877 --> 00:26:33,170
I have to follow
your plan anyway, right?

329
00:26:33,603 --> 00:26:35,603
I'm alone in the world.

330
00:26:35,657 --> 00:26:37,177
I don't have any leverage.

331
00:26:39,710 --> 00:26:41,320
Very smart, Ms. Ramphoei.

332
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:44,543
But don't worry, ma'am.

333
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:47,960
I already prepared your reward.

334
00:26:48,743 --> 00:26:49,840
If you succeed.

335
00:26:50,410 --> 00:26:51,480
Yeah.

336
00:26:54,977 --> 00:26:56,804
If I didn't do as you asked,

337
00:26:56,983 --> 00:26:59,890
I'd probably have ended up
in a ditch like Chaem.

338
00:27:00,083 --> 00:27:02,280
I already told you
I didn't kill her.

339
00:27:04,083 --> 00:27:05,623
You don't have to believe me.

340
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:08,800
And you have to stop
provoking Ms. Malai to doubt me.

341
00:27:09,090 --> 00:27:10,840
If you insist
you didn't kill Chaem,

342
00:27:13,057 --> 00:27:14,990
then I insist
I didn't provoke Malai.

343
00:27:16,409 --> 00:27:18,120
If you don't count
when I was drunk.

344
00:27:20,142 --> 00:27:21,142
If it wasn't you,

345
00:27:21,602 --> 00:27:23,815
then who provoked her to doubt me?

346
00:27:28,802 --> 00:27:29,802
Never mind.

347
00:27:30,030 --> 00:27:31,030
Let's just say

348
00:27:31,223 --> 00:27:34,397
I want to live peacefully
in this house with Ms. Malai.

349
00:27:35,203 --> 00:27:37,776
You just have to stop acting out.

350
00:27:39,523 --> 00:27:41,720
If you weren't still useful to me,

351
00:27:42,043 --> 00:27:43,276
I wouldn't have indulged you.

352
00:27:51,777 --> 00:27:54,930
Don't you have an extra reward
for your son's mother, Dech?

353
00:27:59,650 --> 00:28:00,650
Dech.

354
00:28:00,830 --> 00:28:02,557
You're still young and fit.

355
00:28:02,883 --> 00:28:05,960
You'll go out of your mind
waiting for that nun.

356
00:28:06,770 --> 00:28:08,497
If you and I don't tell,

357
00:28:08,983 --> 00:28:10,240
no one will know.

358
00:28:11,150 --> 00:28:12,150
Ow.

359
00:28:14,843 --> 00:28:16,280
You've got your money.

360
00:28:17,143 --> 00:28:19,430
If you're that hungry, go buy it.

361
00:28:20,730 --> 00:28:22,730
But be careful of diseases.

362
00:28:35,463 --> 00:28:37,200
You're foul-mouthed these days.

363
00:28:48,623 --> 00:28:49,880
I heard your boat capsized

364
00:28:50,110 --> 00:28:51,730
on your way to make merit, Malai?

365
00:28:53,110 --> 00:28:54,110
Yes, ma'am.

366
00:28:54,663 --> 00:28:57,063
Fortunately,
Dech rescued me in time.

367
00:28:58,483 --> 00:29:00,576
From the masters to the servants.

368
00:29:01,197 --> 00:29:02,197
Malai,

369
00:29:02,310 --> 00:29:04,610
you should invite monks
to bless this house.

370
00:29:05,077 --> 00:29:06,077
Ranchuan.

371
00:29:06,657 --> 00:29:07,657
My lord,

372
00:29:08,303 --> 00:29:09,850
I really meant what I said.

373
00:29:09,890 --> 00:29:11,280
Why would you stop me?

374
00:29:12,666 --> 00:29:13,790
I agree, my lord.

375
00:29:14,977 --> 00:29:16,517
When I get the date,

376
00:29:16,857 --> 00:29:19,357
you two are invited
to the ceremony.

377
00:29:24,610 --> 00:29:27,097
The viscount was right
to entrust this house to you.

378
00:29:27,770 --> 00:29:29,080
It's been months.

379
00:29:29,657 --> 00:29:30,920
It still looks the same.

380
00:29:32,477 --> 00:29:33,720
You're right, my lord.

381
00:29:34,177 --> 00:29:35,350
I'm glad it's you.

382
00:29:36,243 --> 00:29:39,280
If it were up to that woman,
we'd have already sold this house.

383
00:29:44,247 --> 00:29:45,600
Since I'm here,

384
00:29:46,073 --> 00:29:49,087
can I take a look at this house's
the income and expenditure records?

385
00:29:49,613 --> 00:29:51,400
I might have some suggestions.

386
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:55,480
Yes, my lord.

387
00:29:57,473 --> 00:29:59,890
Dech's overseeing everything
for the viscount right now.

388
00:30:00,537 --> 00:30:02,724
I look over the books
when I have time.

389
00:30:03,263 --> 00:30:05,363
If you have suggestions,

390
00:30:05,490 --> 00:30:06,560
let me know, my lord.

391
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:10,289
You really are his close servant

392
00:30:10,300 --> 00:30:12,080
who's served him for over a decade.

393
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,960
Having someone trustworthy

394
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:16,480
is a good thing.

395
00:30:18,847 --> 00:30:20,214
Then please come this way.

396
00:30:22,323 --> 00:30:25,436
You go ahead and see
the viscount with Malai.

397
00:30:25,856 --> 00:30:26,856
I'll join you later.

398
00:30:27,237 --> 00:30:28,237
Yes, my lord.

399
00:30:28,390 --> 00:30:29,390
Please.

400
00:30:32,309 --> 00:30:33,360
Let's go, ma'am.

401
00:30:46,730 --> 00:30:48,730
I didn't know
you were educated enough

402
00:30:48,783 --> 00:30:51,197
to keep the books as well as
when the viscount was fine.

403
00:30:51,483 --> 00:30:52,760
If not better.

404
00:30:53,183 --> 00:30:55,183
You're too kind, my lord.

405
00:30:55,317 --> 00:30:59,480
The profit rose after the viscount
received his inheritance, my lord.

406
00:31:02,303 --> 00:31:03,303
Go on.

407
00:31:03,830 --> 00:31:06,197
I bought and fixed old buildings,

408
00:31:06,403 --> 00:31:08,120
then let the government rent them.

409
00:31:08,730 --> 00:31:09,883
As for farms,

410
00:31:09,977 --> 00:31:12,670
I've had them harvested
and sold the produce for income.

411
00:31:12,730 --> 00:31:14,280
Better than letting them overgrow.

412
00:31:16,850 --> 00:31:18,383
You're business smart.

413
00:31:18,823 --> 00:31:20,240
Of course I have to praise you.

414
00:31:21,403 --> 00:31:22,800
It's the viscount's luck

415
00:31:23,083 --> 00:31:24,490
to have such a faithful servant.

416
00:31:25,223 --> 00:31:26,263
Yes, my lord.

417
00:31:49,403 --> 00:31:51,120
You're the only one

418
00:31:51,637 --> 00:31:53,317
who takes good care
of the viscount.

419
00:31:54,430 --> 00:31:55,760
As for Ramphoei,

420
00:31:56,257 --> 00:31:57,760
does she even care?

421
00:31:58,143 --> 00:31:59,743
Let's not talk about her.

422
00:32:00,036 --> 00:32:02,400
As long as she doesn't
cause problems, I'm happy.

423
00:32:03,697 --> 00:32:04,697
True.

424
00:32:04,857 --> 00:32:07,194
The viscount finally has an heir,

425
00:32:07,420 --> 00:32:08,480
instead of...

426
00:32:11,207 --> 00:32:12,907
I apologize, my lord.

427
00:32:13,180 --> 00:32:14,454
I talk too much.

428
00:32:18,437 --> 00:32:19,760
What did he say?

429
00:32:20,550 --> 00:32:21,923
Can you understand?

430
00:32:23,977 --> 00:32:25,800
I struggled at first

431
00:32:26,090 --> 00:32:27,840
to understand his requests.

432
00:32:28,043 --> 00:32:30,400
But I'm getting a hold of it
because I use...

433
00:32:32,970 --> 00:32:33,970
Use what?

434
00:32:34,337 --> 00:32:35,337
Use...

435
00:32:35,430 --> 00:32:37,883
Use my feelings and check the time

436
00:32:38,343 --> 00:32:41,043
what he wants at this hour.

437
00:32:43,603 --> 00:32:44,910
You've been here a while.

438
00:32:45,997 --> 00:32:47,557
I haven't served you snack.

439
00:32:48,010 --> 00:32:49,160
Forgive my manners.

440
00:32:49,710 --> 00:32:52,450
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay. We're family.

441
00:32:52,783 --> 00:32:54,560
Uh, I'll be right back, ma'am.

442
00:33:11,270 --> 00:33:12,510
What do you want, my lord?

443
00:33:20,583 --> 00:33:22,090
What do you want, my lord?

444
00:33:38,543 --> 00:33:40,310
You want these documents?

445
00:34:17,343 --> 00:34:18,343
The letters?

446
00:34:19,443 --> 00:34:20,443
The vowels?

447
00:34:23,990 --> 00:34:28,481
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

448
00:34:28,903 --> 00:34:33,390
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

449
00:34:41,257 --> 00:34:42,257
Dech!

450
00:34:48,870 --> 00:34:49,960
Hello, my lord.

451
00:34:51,923 --> 00:34:53,736
You're probably
talking shop with Dech.

452
00:34:53,903 --> 00:34:55,316
I won't be long, my lord.

453
00:34:57,387 --> 00:35:00,024
Give me my daily allowance.
I have to go out soon.

454
00:35:18,897 --> 00:35:19,897
Wait.

455
00:35:21,483 --> 00:35:22,483
Excuse me.

456
00:35:30,043 --> 00:35:31,680
Is this your month allowance?

457
00:35:34,363 --> 00:35:35,520
Daily allowance.

458
00:35:35,883 --> 00:35:37,440
In case Dech's too afraid to answer.

459
00:35:37,810 --> 00:35:40,320
You're spending this much money?

460
00:35:41,643 --> 00:35:43,000
Why can't I, my lord?

461
00:35:43,417 --> 00:35:45,680
I have a viscount for a husband.

462
00:35:45,983 --> 00:35:48,509
I can't possibly live like a pauper

463
00:35:48,603 --> 00:35:50,680
or people will criticize me.

464
00:35:51,057 --> 00:35:52,616
They'll say you spend money

465
00:35:52,627 --> 00:35:54,720
like someone who forgets
her place, Ramphoei.

466
00:35:55,070 --> 00:35:56,070
My lord,

467
00:35:56,297 --> 00:36:00,530
you can make Ms. Ranchuan
live as humbly as you want.

468
00:36:01,663 --> 00:36:02,663
We all know.

469
00:36:03,083 --> 00:36:05,083
Your position is
lower than your brother's.

470
00:36:05,183 --> 00:36:06,960
And you got none of the fortune.

471
00:36:07,417 --> 00:36:09,680
It's natural for you
to know your place.

472
00:36:11,577 --> 00:36:12,664
Ms. Ramphoei,

473
00:36:13,257 --> 00:36:14,440
apologize right now.

474
00:36:14,523 --> 00:36:16,703
Jeez, sorry, Dech.

475
00:36:17,070 --> 00:36:19,777
I don't consider myself
related to...

476
00:36:19,910 --> 00:36:21,000
poor people.

477
00:36:22,297 --> 00:36:25,137
I asked you for help once

478
00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:27,143
but you ignored me.

479
00:36:27,563 --> 00:36:29,760
I don't have to respect you either.

480
00:36:30,563 --> 00:36:31,960
Goodbye, my lord.

481
00:36:44,570 --> 00:36:47,403
I apologize for Ms. Ramphoei
disrespecting you, my lord.

482
00:36:47,823 --> 00:36:50,040
Forget it. She was born wicked.

483
00:36:50,790 --> 00:36:52,040
Nothing will improve her.

484
00:36:52,450 --> 00:36:55,157
It's a shame the viscount
took a degenerate as a mistress.

485
00:36:57,897 --> 00:36:58,897
Let's get back to work.

486
00:36:59,617 --> 00:37:00,617
Yes, sir.

487
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:10,190
So most of the house's expenditure

488
00:37:10,403 --> 00:37:12,290
is Ramphoei's allowance?

489
00:37:14,017 --> 00:37:16,017
Because the other
expenses look reasonable.

490
00:37:17,797 --> 00:37:18,797
Yes, my lord.

491
00:37:19,003 --> 00:37:21,383
In exchange for Ms. Ramphoei
no longer causing problems

492
00:37:21,502 --> 00:37:22,536
and harassing people,

493
00:37:23,050 --> 00:37:24,160
I have to pay her.

494
00:37:24,490 --> 00:37:25,490
I understand.

495
00:37:46,650 --> 00:37:47,650
The letters?

496
00:37:48,777 --> 00:37:49,777
The vowels?

497
00:37:54,530 --> 00:37:56,350
You want to talk to me, my lord?

498
00:38:03,560 --> 00:38:05,120
We finally understand each other.

499
00:38:05,723 --> 00:38:07,280
Too bad Malai's not here.

500
00:38:07,463 --> 00:38:09,000
Or I would have understood faster.

501
00:38:09,903 --> 00:38:10,903
But earlier,

502
00:38:11,257 --> 00:38:13,437
why didn't she say
there was something like this?

503
00:38:14,561 --> 00:38:16,442
How do we start?

504
00:38:19,823 --> 00:38:21,363
The snack's ready, Ms...

505
00:38:22,230 --> 00:38:23,230
Malai.

506
00:38:23,597 --> 00:38:24,624
Come help me.

507
00:38:24,823 --> 00:38:26,160
How do you use this?

508
00:38:31,510 --> 00:38:32,510
Uh..

509
00:38:32,957 --> 00:38:33,957
Ms. Ranchuan.

510
00:38:36,077 --> 00:38:37,077
What have you been...

511
00:38:37,850 --> 00:38:39,917
saying to the viscount, ma'am?

512
00:38:40,210 --> 00:38:41,210
Nothing yet.

513
00:38:42,630 --> 00:38:45,120
It took me a while
to understand his request.

514
00:38:47,377 --> 00:38:49,377
Did you make this table yourself?

515
00:38:49,757 --> 00:38:50,757
So...

516
00:38:51,217 --> 00:38:52,576
What have you two talked about?

517
00:38:53,243 --> 00:38:54,243
Not a lot, ma'am.

518
00:38:54,937 --> 00:38:57,210
I let His Lordship look at

519
00:38:57,490 --> 00:38:59,840
each letter and watch his eyes

520
00:38:59,903 --> 00:39:01,440
if it's the right letter,

521
00:39:01,897 --> 00:39:03,444
then I compound each word.

522
00:39:03,930 --> 00:39:06,000
- But I stopped using this method.
- Eh?

523
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:07,840
Why?

524
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:10,760
Uh...

525
00:39:11,183 --> 00:39:12,830
It took a lot of time and...

526
00:39:12,923 --> 00:39:14,350
sometimes I got the wrong words.

527
00:39:14,590 --> 00:39:15,843
So I misunderstood him.

528
00:39:16,109 --> 00:39:18,577
The method I told you earlier
is a lot better.

529
00:39:19,456 --> 00:39:20,456
No wonder.

530
00:39:20,997 --> 00:39:24,783
I'm sorry I didn't tell you
earlier about this method.

531
00:39:25,017 --> 00:39:27,017
Don't mention it. It's nothing.

532
00:39:27,137 --> 00:39:28,137
I understand.

533
00:39:28,170 --> 00:39:31,440
If you get the words wrong
and cause misunderstanding,

534
00:39:32,203 --> 00:39:33,720
things will be hectic.

535
00:39:43,157 --> 00:39:44,157
My lord.

536
00:39:44,650 --> 00:39:45,650
How is he?

537
00:39:48,010 --> 00:39:49,197
Like you see, my lord.

538
00:39:49,429 --> 00:39:51,823
He knows what's going on
but he can't respond.

539
00:39:54,023 --> 00:39:57,443
My lord, Malai said
she prepared snack for us.

540
00:39:57,670 --> 00:39:59,350
Would you like that now?

541
00:39:59,843 --> 00:40:00,843
Sure.

542
00:40:02,850 --> 00:40:03,917
This way, please.

543
00:40:27,437 --> 00:40:29,280
I'm sorry, my lord,

544
00:40:29,563 --> 00:40:30,563
for stopping you.

545
00:40:32,183 --> 00:40:35,596
I can't let you accuse Dech
